Detailed Description

cvmx_tra::_ctl

TRA_CTL = Trace Buffer Control

Description:

Notes: It is illegal to change the values of WRAP, TRIG_CTL, IGNORE_O while tracing (i.e. when ENA=1). Note that the following fields are present only in chip revisions beginning with pass2: IGNORE_O
